HOUSING AUTHORITY
v.
PARTEE. No. 183P08. Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 11, 2008. Adam Shestak, for Housing Authority. John Roseboro, for Housing Authority.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 24th day of April 2008 by Defendant for Temporary Stay:

"Motion for Stay dissolved by order of the Court in conference this the 11th day of June 2008."
